originalText.text: Michelle is an excellent aesthetician. She takes times to understand her clients concerns, desired outcomes, and skin type to create the best treatment plan. She has a gentle hand and watchful eye to make sure that just the right procedure is skillfully executed. I personally had micro needling done on both my face and scalp. You will leave feeling more youthful, revitalized and confident. Skin Compleet is the only place you need for your skin care needs.

originalText.text: OMG! My skin is glowing! I had a micro needling treatment by Michelle 2 months ago. I was hesitant because I heard it hurts and a few days down time but Michelle used numbing cream which took away any discomfort. My skin was red for 3 days but I purchased oxygenetics make which Michelle applied to my skin after the treatment. This make up not inly had amazing coverage but it also promotes healing of your skin!!
